td boot-test SSH key — TEST FIXTURE ONLY.

td_test_ed25519{,.pub} is a throwaway ed25519 keypair used solely by
tests/boot.scm to prove that key-based SSH login to the td guest works and
that a remote command's output is captured. It is a committed fixture so the
build stays reproducible (a key generated at build time would not be).

It is NOT provisioned into the shipped system: the test authorizes it only on
a test-only operating-system overlay (see tests/boot.scm). The frozen
`td-system` (and its qcow2/OCI images, the M4/M5 differential oracle) does not
contain this account or key. The private key grants no access to anything but
an ephemeral test VM that is wiped on reset. Do not reuse it for anything.
